title: Packers-Eagles, play calling, and the Blazing 5
itunes:title: Packers-Eagles, play calling, and the Blazing 5
description:
Colin discusses the Packers-Eagles game, why QB Aaron Rodgers is great, why he doesn't like questioning play calling, and his Blazing 5 picks for the weekend. Guests include Greg Jennings, Brady Poppinga, Albert Breer, Brandon Boykin, and Jason McIntyre.
